      "end": 44.03,
      "text": "여성 운동가들의 유쾌한 반란을 그리고 있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.03,
      "end": 45.87,
      "text": "미스 비헤비어"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.87,
      "end": 47.57,
      "text": "굿모닝 크리스"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.57,
      "end": 48.39,
      "text": "굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.39,
      "end": 49.09,
      "text": "로라"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.09,
      "end": 49.69,
      "text": "야"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.69,
      "end": 53.21,
      "text": "I think this movie is so meaningful misbehavior."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.47,
      "end": 53.87,
      "text": "아하"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.87,
      "end": 56.63,
      "text": "First of all, it is based on a true story."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.83,
      "end": 57.31,
      "text": "It is."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.57,
      "end": 59.45,
      "text": "이게 사실에 근거한 영화잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.15,
      "end": 62.55,
      "text": "비록 이 사건은 happened a long time ago."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.77,
      "end": 63.97,
      "text": "Back in the 70s."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.03,
      "end": 66.95,
      "text": "Yes, but it can still affect the present time."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.03,
      "end": 67.35,
      "text": "Sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.65,
      "end": 69.07,
      "text": "History is all connected."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.31,
      "end": 69.65,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.79,
      "end": 71.01,
      "text": "What happened back then"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.01,
      "end": 73.83,
      "text": "is connected to what is happening right now."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.87,
      "end": 74.35,
      "text": "맞습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.35,
      "end": 75.73,
      "text": "Which is connected to the future."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.87,
      "end": 76.15,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.15,
      "end": 77.55,
      "text": "It's all one big story."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.63,
      "end": 77.87,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.21,
      "end": 80.03,
      "text": "Oh, history는 정말 it's alive."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.27,
      "end": 81.61,
      "text": "이렇게 표현할 수도 있을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.63,
      "end": 81.99,
      "text": "Definitely."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.31,
      "end": 83.17,
      "text": "It's living."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.45,
      "end": 84.25,
      "text": "아, 멋집니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.31,
      "end": 85.05,
      "text": "Just like language."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.15,
      "end": 85.97,
      "text": "Yeah, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.13,
      "end": 87.01,
      "text": "Language is alive."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.79,
      "end": 90.93,
      "text": "근데 우리의 주인공 셀리가요."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.29,
      "end": 93.03,
      "text": "이런 인터뷰를 했대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.19,
      "end": 93.95,
      "text": "제가 한번 읽어드릴게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.21,
      "end": 94.47,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.47,
      "end": 101.71,
      "text": "Each generation must find its own way of dealing with the struggle with political and social injustice."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.39,
      "end": 104.01,
      "text": "Very wise words."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.45,
      "end": 107.23,
      "text": "So every generation has a job to do."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.37,
      "end": 107.69,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.81,
      "end": 108.67,
      "text": "It never ends."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.67,
      "end": 109.89,
      "text": "Like history."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.89,
      "end": 110.01,
      "text": "Like history."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.01,
      "end": 110.29,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.79,
      "end": 115.13,
      "text": "어느 시대이든 아니면 어느 국가이든지 간에 문제는 있기 마련이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.31,
      "end": 116.61,
      "text": "하지만 우리 인류는 어때요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.91,
      "end": 121.27,
      "text": "항상 그것을 위해서 투쟁하고, 발전시키고, 보완시키고."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.39,
      "end": 124.55,
      "text": "Oh, you're sounding passionate."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.41,
      "end": 127.47,
      "text": "영화에 영향을 받았나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.59,
      "end": 128.03,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.67,
      "end": 130.93,
      "text": "She also said, Sally said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.93,
      "end": 133.31,
      "text": "there's still a great deal to do"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.31,
      "end": 136.11,
      "text": "and so many young women today are active"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.11,
      "end": 138.13,
      "text": "and in a different way."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.37,
      "end": 140.11,
      "text": "We are still hopeful."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.39,
      "end": 140.79,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.25,
      "end": 142.23,
      "text": "진짜 멋집니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.85,
      "end": 144.59,
      "text": "자, 그럼 오늘 내용 먼저 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.59,
      "end": 147.53,
      "text": "So, topics for your dissertations."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.93,
      "end": 148.51,
      "text": "How are you getting on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.89,
      "end": 149.63,
      "text": "No, no, sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.79,
      "end": 152.77,
      "text": "The industrial revolution in Scotland."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.31,
      "end": 153.95,
      "text": "Good choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.65,
      "end": 154.93,
      "text": "Sally."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.69,
      "end": 159.01,
      "text": "I was thinking about looking at it from the point of view of women workers."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.99,
      "end": 160.93,
      "text": "It's a bit niche."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.71,
      "end": 162.91,
      "text": "You might want to rethink."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.85,
      "end": 165.15,
      "text": "Oh, 지금 Sally가요."
    },
    {
      "start": 165.43,
      "end": 169.23,
      "text": "논문 주제를 특히 여성 노동자에 대해서 쓰겠다고 했더니"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.23,
      "end": 170.11,
      "text": "지도교수가"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.11,
      "end": 174.53,
      "text": "His reaction is not so positive."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.69,
      "end": 175.65,
      "text": "네, 느끼셨죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.87,
      "end": 179.29,
      "text": "재고해봐라 라고 하는 그런 상황이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 179.45,
      "end": 181.25,
      "text": "So, they're sitting around in a circle."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.25,
      "end": 184.61,
      "text": "The professor with his graduate students."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.51,
      "end": 189.89,
      "text": "And the biggest thing, the biggest pain or headache"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.89,
      "end": 191.15,
      "text": "in graduate school"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.15,
      "end": 192.81,
      "text": "is to write a thesis"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.81,
      "end": 194.49,
      "text": "or a dissertation."
    },
    {
      "start": 194.75,
      "end": 195.15,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 195.21,
      "end": 197.13,
      "text": "That very, very long paper"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.13,
      "end": 200.39,
      "text": "that takes so much time to write."
    },
    {
      "start": 200.77,
      "end": 203.85,
      "text": "So, have you ever had such an experience?"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.85,
      "end": 209.07,
      "text": "In my undergrad, we write a sort of dissertation"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.07,
      "end": 209.41,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.57,
      "end": 211.85,
      "text": "But it's not 50 pages long."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.09,
      "end": 214.01,
      "text": "I think it was like 20 maybe?"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.17,
      "end": 214.91,
      "text": "20 to 30?"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.19,
      "end": 215.57,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.77,
      "end": 217.63,
      "text": "20장, 30장 쓰는 것도 힘들죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.63,
      "end": 220.57,
      "text": "That was the longest paper I had ever written."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.57,
      "end": 221.03,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.63,
      "end": 222.01,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.13,
      "end": 223.65,
      "text": "And it took a lot of research."
    },
    {
      "start": 223.85,
      "end": 224.09,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.15,
      "end": 225.33,
      "text": "A lot of long nights."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.63,
      "end": 225.83,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.23,
      "end": 226.91,
      "text": "맞습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.19,
      "end": 227.47,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.47,
      "end": 229.01,
      "text": "이제 논문 주제를 고르고"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.01,
      "end": 231.83,
      "text": "그 주제를 교수님의 마음에"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.83,
      "end": 234.39,
      "text": "좀 흡족한 주제를 고른다라는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.39,
      "end": 237.45,
      "text": "굉장히 힘들고 떨리는 그런 작업이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.45,
      "end": 239.95,
      "text": "자, 일단 내용을 잘 이해하기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.95,
      "end": 241.45,
      "text": "단어들을 미리 알아볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.35,
      "end": 243.23,
      "text": "Dissertations"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.23,
      "end": 244.83,
      "text": "Dissertations"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.83,
      "end": 245.55,
      "text": "들리셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.69,
      "end": 247.57,
      "text": "논문에 관련된 단어입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 247.83,
      "end": 248.01,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.09,
      "end": 248.95,
      "text": "Just like a thesis."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.19,
      "end": 249.47,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.63,
      "end": 249.89,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.03,
      "end": 251.05,
      "text": "Similar to a thesis."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.53,
      "end": 252.75,
      "text": "Thesis라고도 할 수 있고"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.75,
      "end": 255.35,
      "text": "Dissertations라고도 이야기를 할 수가 있죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.17,
      "end": 256.61,
      "text": "Niche"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.61,
      "end": 258.93,
      "text": "Niche는 무슨 의미냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.93,
      "end": 259.61,
      "text": "Niche"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.61,
      "end": 262.39,
      "text": "좀 다양하게 의미가 활용이 가능한데"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.39,
      "end": 264.03,
      "text": "뭐 틈새라든지"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.03,
      "end": 266.31,
      "text": "아니면 국한적인, 제한적인"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.31,
      "end": 267.95,
      "text": "이라는 의미로도 쓰일 수가 있고"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.95,
      "end": 269.35,
      "text": "Usually it's a good meaning."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.47,
      "end": 269.75,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.97,
      "end": 271.01,
      "text": "Like what's your niche?"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.25,
      "end": 272.93,
      "text": "What's your special area?"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.93,
      "end": 273.33,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.47,
      "end": 275.31,
      "text": "That you are an expert in."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.39,
      "end": 275.87,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.23,
      "end": 277.69,
      "text": "너에게 딱 맞는 자리가"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.69,
      "end": 278.67,
      "text": "바로 무엇일까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.91,
      "end": 281.05,
      "text": "라는 그런 뉘앙스를 전달할 때도"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.05,
      "end": 282.25,
      "text": "이 Niche라는 단어를"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.25,
      "end": 283.97,
      "text": "사용을 할 수가 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.13,
      "end": 284.99,
      "text": "꼭 맞는 자리"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.99,
      "end": 285.65,
      "text": "이와 같이요."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.73,
      "end": 287.33,
      "text": "But here it's not so positive"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.33,
      "end": 288.67,
      "text": "in this conversation."
    },
    {
      "start": 288.73,
      "end": 289.07,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.19,
      "end": 290.83,
      "text": "Rethink"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.83,
      "end": 293.75,
      "text": "아, 이거는 대부분 다 알고 계실 것 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.75,
      "end": 294.73,
      "text": "Rethink"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.73,
      "end": 295.03,
      "text": "그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 295.27,
      "end": 296.29,
      "text": "이걸 풀어서 이야기하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.29,
      "end": 297.07,
      "text": "Think again"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.07,
      "end": 298.21,
      "text": "이것과도 같이"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.21,
      "end": 300.01,
      "text": "생각하실 수 있겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.17,
      "end": 301.25,
      "text": "Think it over again."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.25,
      "end": 301.81,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.99,
      "end": 303.71,
      "text": "다시 생각하다, 재고하다"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.71,
      "end": 304.73,
      "text": "라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.13,
      "end": 305.89,
      "text": "그러면 이 내용"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.89,
      "end": 306.83,
      "text": "다시 한번 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 306.83,
      "end": 327.09,
      "text": "다시 들어도"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.09,
      "end": 329.65,
      "text": "정말 떨리는 순간이 아닐 수가 없었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 329.65,
      "end": 332.45,
      "text": "And his pronunciation of niche"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.45,
      "end": 333.53,
      "text": "is niche."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.79,
      "end": 334.07,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.29,
      "end": 334.81,
      "text": "Did you hear that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.97,
      "end": 335.21,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.59,
      "end": 336.15,
      "text": "그래서 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 336.15,
      "end": 337.43,
      "text": "좀 더 뭔가"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.43,
      "end": 339.67,
      "text": "고급스럽게"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.67,
      "end": 341.07,
      "text": "일부러 발음을 하는 건가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.67,
      "end": 342.83,
      "text": "It sounded, yeah,"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.97,
      "end": 344.21,
      "text": "very 고급스럽게"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.21,
      "end": 344.49,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.49,
      "end": 345.79,
      "text": "Very sophisticated"
    },
