      "start": 599.48,
      "end": 600.72,
      "text": "in that topic."
    },
    {
      "start": 601.18,
      "end": 602.26,
      "text": "So rethink it."
    },
    {
      "start": 602.38,
      "end": 603.26,
      "text": "Think it over again."
    },
    {
      "start": 603.5,
      "end": 605.24,
      "text": "And Sally is feeling"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.24,
      "end": 606.58,
      "text": "devastated."
    },
    {
      "start": 606.58,
      "end": 607.46,
      "text": "그러게 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 607.58,
      "end": 608.32,
      "text": "She's feeling down."
    },
    {
      "start": 608.7,
      "end": 609.8,
      "text": "그나저나 이렇게"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.8,
      "end": 611.74,
      "text": "학생들의 부류에는요."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.82,
      "end": 612.8,
      "text": "이렇게 세 가지 종류가"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.8,
      "end": 613.48,
      "text": "있는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.14,
      "end": 614.74,
      "text": "첫 번째는"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.74,
      "end": 616.02,
      "text": "아직 못했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.6,
      "end": 617.26,
      "text": "이런 종류."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.34,
      "end": 617.98,
      "text": "두 번째는"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.98,
      "end": 620.4,
      "text": "잘 돼갑니다 라고 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.4,
      "end": 620.88,
      "text": "교수님한테"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.88,
      "end": 621.92,
      "text": "칭찬을 받는 부류."
    },
    {
      "start": 622.28,
      "end": 623.04,
      "text": "세 번째로는"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.04,
      "end": 624.18,
      "text": "다시 생각해 보게"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.18,
      "end": 624.82,
      "text": "라고 해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.82,
      "end": 625.9,
      "text": "가슴이 무너지는"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.9,
      "end": 626.92,
      "text": "그런 경험을 하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.92,
      "end": 628.62,
      "text": "학생들 부류가 있을 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 628.62,
      "end": 630.1,
      "text": "Which one do you"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.1,
      "end": 630.56,
      "text": "속해요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.8,
      "end": 631.74,
      "text": "Which one do you belong in?"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.88,
      "end": 632.78,
      "text": "저는 주로"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.78,
      "end": 633.52,
      "text": "number two"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.52,
      "end": 635.28,
      "text": "잘 돼갑니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 635.74,
      "end": 636.98,
      "text": "칭찬받는 학생"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.98,
      "end": 637.46,
      "text": "Jeremy"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.46,
      "end": 639.38,
      "text": "무조건 칭찬받으려고"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.38,
      "end": 640.44,
      "text": "딱 넘길게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 640.74,
      "end": 641.84,
      "text": "다시 한번 들어 보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 643.04,
      "end": 645.14,
      "text": "So topics for your dissertations."
    },
    {
      "start": 645.56,
      "end": 646.14,
      "text": "How are you getting on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.5,
      "end": 647.26,
      "text": "No, no, sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 648.18,
      "end": 649.96,
      "text": "The industrial revolution"
    },
    {
      "start": 649.96,
      "end": 650.4,
      "text": "in Scotland."
    },
    {
      "start": 650.92,
      "end": 651.58,
      "text": "Good choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 652.28,
      "end": 652.56,
      "text": "Sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 653.32,
      "end": 654.64,
      "text": "I was thinking about"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.64,
      "end": 655.16,
      "text": "looking at it"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.16,
      "end": 655.8,
      "text": "from the point of view"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.8,
      "end": 656.64,
      "text": "of women workers."
    },
    {
      "start": 657.63,
      "end": 658.59,
      "text": "It's a bit niche."
    },
    {
      "start": 659.31,
      "end": 660.51,
      "text": "You might want to rethink."
    },
    {
      "start": 661.7,
      "end": 662.72,
      "text": "오늘 장면을"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.72,
      "end": 663.68,
      "text": "이렇게 듣다 보니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 663.76,
      "end": 665.32,
      "text": "이게 오늘 내용과는"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.32,
      "end": 666.36,
      "text": "좀 상관은 없지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.36,
      "end": 667.9,
      "text": "I'm thinking of"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.9,
      "end": 668.78,
      "text": "Professor Kim"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.78,
      "end": 669.92,
      "text": "whom I really, really"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.92,
      "end": 671.02,
      "text": "admire a lot."
    },
    {
      "start": 671.24,
      "end": 672.54,
      "text": "Was that your professor?"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.74,
      "end": 673.36,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 673.38,
      "end": 674.5,
      "text": "Oh, from college."
    },
    {
      "start": 675.24,
      "end": 676.4,
      "text": "Yeah, graduate school에"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.4,
      "end": 678.46,
      "text": "제가 정말 존경하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.46,
      "end": 679.88,
      "text": "교수님이 또 생각이 나네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 679.98,
      "end": 680.54,
      "text": "Did you write"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.54,
      "end": 681.88,
      "text": "a dissertation for him?"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.36,
      "end": 682.92,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 683.66,
      "end": 683.92,
      "text": "특히"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.92,
      "end": 685.12,
      "text": "master's degree"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.12,
      "end": 685.9,
      "text": "를 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.9,
      "end": 688.14,
      "text": "master's thesis를"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.14,
      "end": 689.7,
      "text": "썼던 기억이"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.7,
      "end": 690.72,
      "text": "또 새록새록 납니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 690.92,
      "end": 692.08,
      "text": "I hope he was more supportive"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.08,
      "end": 693.06,
      "text": "than this professor"
    },
    {
      "start": 693.06,
      "end": 693.96,
      "text": "was to Sally."
    },
    {
      "start": 694.18,
      "end": 694.68,
      "text": "Sure, sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 694.92,
      "end": 695.12,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 695.5,
      "end": 695.96,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 696.18,
      "end": 697.5,
      "text": "오늘 screen english는"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.5,
      "end": 698.24,
      "text": "여기서 마무리"
    }
  ]
}